SELECT [t].[PostId] AS [Id], [t].[Title], [t].[Slug], [t].[Author], COALESCE([c].[Name], N'Uncategorized') AS [Category], [t].[CreateAt] AS [CreatedAt], [t].[Description], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Comments] AS [c0]
    WHERE [t].[PostId] = [c0].[PostId]) AS [CommentsCount]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[PostId], [p].[Author], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreateAt], [p].[Description], [p].[Slug], [p].[Title]
    FROM [Posts] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[PostId]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[PostId]
